{"tid":756594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屢爆醜聞　港鐵高層疑遭執法部門調查被解僱","createTime":"2018-07-26T07:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T15:18:48.000Z","uid":166893,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e80d1768ede4623ef67ca1e9cc80b486a3e8b43f","tid":756594,"uid":166893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"屢爆醜聞　港鐵高層疑遭執法部門調查被解僱<br />\n<br />\n近日爆出多宗醜聞的港鐵，傳出有高層被執法部門調查而遭解僱。消息指，港鐵數名經理級人員被「炒魷魚」，其中一人負責內地事務，他昨日(25日)遭港鐵即時解僱，餘下數名經理級人員亦陸續接獲通知，在保安人員陪同下送離港鐵九龍灣總部的辦事處。東網正向港鐵了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n廉政公署發言人表示，根據政策，廉署一般不會評論個別事件。根據該署法定職責，若接獲貪污投訴，如有足夠資料，該署必定會按既定程序依法跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180726/bkn-20180726123303455-0726_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180726%2Fbkn-20180726123303455-0726_00822_001.html&d=OVBuK%2BeWhGt9hbVL8e0DLMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=668d68b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180726/bkn-20180726123303455-0726_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3cc0570f5c485b4465bb09d5490736621e43f764","tid":756594,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"馬仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f6ed026643cd5da6b5f17fc2e27d6500ddf4b","tid":756594,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"經理級唔係叫中層咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed78d7a0d00869712bd887f50e9b5f5e1b7ffca","tid":756594,"uid":166893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a60f6ed026643cd5da6b5f17fc2e27d6500ddf4b","tid":756594,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"經理級唔係叫中層咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"系基層員工"},{"pid":"96a6ff253206b03b3f8873d8